dcterms:description: The MoNuSeg dataset consists of a 30-image training set and a 14-image testing set, with images of size 1000x1000 sampled from different whole slide images of multiple organs. The dataset includes pixel-level annotation for the nuclei semantic segmentation problem.
dcterms:title: MoNuSeg

dcterms:description: The TNBC dataset is comprised of 50 histopathology images of size 512x512 without any specific testing set. It includes pixel-level annotation for the nuclei semantic segmentation problem.
dcterms:title: TNBC

dcterms:description: The piriform cortex EM dataset contains four stacks of EM images with slice image sizes of 255x255, 512x512, 512x512, and 256x256, respectively. It is used for EM membrane segmentation.
dcterms:title: piriform cortex EM dataset

dcterms:description: The whole slide image dataset was constructed from a whole slide image collected by MICCAI15 CBTC. It includes 2900 patches of size 512x512 at a 40x magnification level.
dcterms:title: Whole slide image dataset from MICCAI15 CBTC
